<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-49-1169 </DOCNO><TEXT>Since the energy requirement of the brain is supplied almost exclusivelyby glucose, the functional state of the tissue can be estimated and quantitativelydemonstrated by reference to the glucose metabolism. The investigationmethod in most widespread use employs /sup 18/F-fluoro-2-deoxy-D-glucose(/sup 18/FDG) for quantitative imaging of the glucose metabolism by meansof PET.</TEXT></DOC>